</style>通过一个函数，例如</p><p><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" Y = A L^{1-\alpha} K^{\alpha} "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.182em;">Y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.584em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.04em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.584em; padding-left: 0.144em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>式中， <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" L "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span></span></span></span> 、 <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" K "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span></span></span></span></span>分别表示全国劳动力总量和资本存量， <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 0 < \alpha < 1 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span>为参数， <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" A "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>为全要素生产率，以下简称TFP。如果两个国家拥有相同的资本存量和劳动力，但其中一个国家的经济产出更高，我们就说这个国家的全要素生产率更高。</p><p>当然，同样的原则适用于一般情况，而不仅仅是针对这种特定的功能形式以及劳动力和资本投入。如果我们有一些经济相关的投入<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" f_1, f_2, \ldots, f_n "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">…</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （有时称为<em>生产要素</em>），我们可以想象一个模型，其中一个国家的经济产出由下式给出</p><p><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" Y = A H(f_1, f_2, \ldots, f_n) "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.182em;">Y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">…</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>对于某些函数<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" H "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。在这种情况下，TFP <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" A "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>只是“关闭模型”的一个因素： <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" f_i "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">输入</span></span></span><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">fi</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的变化未解释的输出变化将自动由<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" A "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>的变化解释。对于特定的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" H "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，我们可以将<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" A = Y/H "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.182em;">Y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span></span></span></span></span>视为经济生产率的衡量标准，它控制了“明显因素”，例如劳动力或资本存量的变化。当然，正确选择<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" H "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span></span></span></span></span>非常重要：我们不想使用随机的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" H "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，而是实际由数据告知的 H 。稍后我将详细讨论我们如何做到这一点。</p><p>例如，如果一个国家的全要素生产率随着时间的推移而增加，则表明该国的产出正在上升，原因是我们模型之外的因素。如果我们的模型只有劳动力和资本存量，也许该国工人的质量已经提高：他们拥有更多的<em>人力资本</em>，即使他们拥有相同数量的人口，因为每个人的平均生产力更高。可能是该国的机构得到了改进，这使它们能够更有效地利用现有资源。模型之外的任何内容都会进入 TFP，这就是为什么它有时被称为“垃圾桶统计数据”。</p><p>重要的是，TFP 这个概念只有<em>相对于模型</em>才有意义，特别是相对于我们选择在模型中考虑的生产要素集合而言。一个国家不存在“绝对TFP”，因为TFP是一个潜变量，其值取决于模型的设定。尽管如此，全要素生产率仍经常被用作技术进步的指标，因为我们直觉地认为，更好的技术应该涉及劳动力、资本和人才的原始积累以外的其他东西。 <a href="https://www.nber.org/system/files/working_papers/w23782/w23782.pdf">Bloom 等人使用了这种方法。 (2020)</a> ，著名的“想法越来越难找到了吗？”纸，专门针对美国。 <a href="https://guzey.com/economics/bloom/#appendix-e-the-us-regressed-technologically-between-1973-and-1982">古泽等人。 （2021）</a>在这一点上批评了他们。</p><h2>全要素生产率下降之谜</h2><p>现在，我们来谈谈帖子标题中的问题。看看下面的图： </p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/4SsoZLYk6efXFWzY5/dohujhmzffqezo2awqww" alt="中国全要素生产率"></p><p>根据该图，中国 1956 年的全要素生产率（当时其人均贫困率低于大多数非洲国家）高于 2019 年！这里发生了什么？</p><p>无论我们如何解释这种说法，说中国在技术上倒退都是没有意义的。今天的中国比1956年拥有更好的物理技术和社会技术（协调机制<em>等</em>）。然而，图表的说法恰恰相反，因此这里似乎存在一些需要解释的差异。当然，我们不想在不了解它是如何构建的情况下将这个系列插入某种技术进步模型中。</p><p>此外，这些难题并非中国独有。自 20 世纪 70 年代初以来，意大利的 TFP 似乎也在下降，而加拿大的 TFP 则持平。这里究竟发生了什么？</p><h2>这些数据是如何构建的？</h2><p>圣路易斯联邦储备银行从<a href="https://www.rug.nl/ggdc/productivity/pwt/">宾夕法尼亚大学世界表</a>中获取这些数据，这是一个数据收集项目，将不同时间和不同国家的经济数据制成表格。他们最新版本的 Excel 电子表格版本大小为 6.4 MB，因此其中有大量数据。除了将更容易衡量的数据（例如 GDP 和人口）制成表格外，他们还在最近发布的版本中报告了 TFP 的估计值。</p><p>首先我们来说一下他们所使用的生产要素。他们对各国的资本存量进行了衡量，并用其来定义<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" K "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span></span></span></span></span> ；他们对劳动力有几个衡量标准：人口规模、就业人口的比例以及就业人员每年平均工作多少小时。除此之外，他们还有一个“人力资本”衡量标准，该衡量标准应该可以解释工人生产率的变化，他们通过观察该国人民的教育程度并将其与相关文献的估计相结合来构建这一衡量标准。多少年的教育值得多少生产率的提高。这将作为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" L "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L 的</span></span></span></span></span></span>乘数添加到数据中，因此受教育程度较高的工人在加权劳动投入指标中的比重更大。</p><p>现在，我们来谈谈他们如何应对<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" H "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span></span></span></span></span>未知的情况。他们的确切方法比我在这里解释的简单版本要复杂一些，但它们在精神上是相似的，并且在应用于纵向数据时给出非常相似的结果，所以我将在这里坚持我的版本。</p><p>如果我们知道<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" Y = A H(f_1, f_2, \ldots, f_n) "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.182em;">Y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">…</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span>成立（根据定义它确实如此），那么只需使用链式法则即可得出</p><p><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \frac{1}{Y} \frac{dY}{dt} = \frac{1}{A} \frac{dA}{dt} + \frac{1}{Y} \sum_{k=1}^n \frac{\partial Y}{\partial f_k} \frac{df_k}{dt} "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.963em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 0.963em; top: -1.368em;"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 0.963em; bottom: -0.772em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.182em;">是</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.963em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.14em; vertical-align: -0.772em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.486em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 1.486em; top: -1.396em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">dYdt</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.182em;">_</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 1.486em; bottom: -0.795em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">_</span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.486em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.191em; vertical-align: -0.795em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.95em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 0.95em; top: -1.368em;"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1A</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 0.95em; bottom: -0.806em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">_</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.95em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.174em; vertical-align: -0.806em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.473em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 1.473em; top: -1.418em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mj