 class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">>;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span></span></span></span></span>和所有<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" L, K "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">、</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，我们有</p><p><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" H(rL, rK) = r H(L, K) "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.057em;">H</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>这意味着对两边的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" r "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span></span></span></span></span>求导时有<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \alpha_K = 1 - \alpha_L "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。这为他们提供了足够的信息来计算<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" A "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>的纵向索引，如上所述。</p><h2>可能会出什么问题？</h2><p>在进行取证分析以找出该计算违反直觉的结果背后的罪魁祸首时，我确定了两个看起来可疑的地方：</p><ol><li>人力资本对劳动力做出的调整。</li><li>假设<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \alpha_K = 1 - \alpha_L "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</li></ol><p>这两种因素都导致大多数国家的全要素生产率增长低于应有水平。更改计算的这些部分会得到以下结果： </p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/4SsoZLYk6efXFWzY5/lzyieqbog1vlx2bfgvbc" alt="中国-tfp-计算"></p><p>这里，“hc”表示人力资本调整，而“csh_ Correction”的包含决定了我们是直接将资本份额估计为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 1 - \alpha_L "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>还是我们是否在上面应用另一个修正（我将很快讨论）。</p><p> “hc + labsh + avh”应该重现 Penn World Table 数据集的结果，我们可以看到这是成功的，因为两条曲线完全重合。通过删除“hc”（人力资本调整）并添加“csh_ Correction”（资本份额修正）来解决第（1）和（2）点的累积影响是将 TFP 估计值转移到曲线“csh_ Correction + labsh + avh”。正如你所看到的，如果我们以此曲线作为我们的 TFP 估算值，那么自 1970 年以来，中国的 TFP 似乎增长了 2.36 倍，而不是保持持平！</p><p>现在，让我们更详细地讨论（1）和（2）。</p><h3>人力资本调整</h3><p>宾夕法尼亚大学世界表论文没有详细描述他们如何计算数据集中的人力资本乘数。他们表示，他们从<a href="http://www.barrolee.com/">Barro 和 Lee (2013)</a>中获取了不同年龄组的小学、中学和高等教育完成情况的数据，并将这些数据与教育回报的一些估计相结合（例如，每年收入增加 10%）。这些不同的教育时期。然而，我无法找到他们用于计算的教育年限的确切回报。</p><p>尽管如此，我们还是可以得到一些粗略的估计。 <a href="http://www.barrolee.com/">Barro 和 Lee（2013）的</a>数据集显示，从 1956 年到 2015 年，25 岁​​至 64 岁中国人口的平均受教育年限增加了约 7 年。将其与报告中报告的人力资本指数<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \approx 2.22 "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">约</span></span><span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2.22</span></span></span></span></span></span>倍的增长相结合。同一时期的 PWT 表明，他们假设教育的社会回报约为</p><p><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \frac{\log(2.22)}{7} \approx 11.4 \%/\text{year} "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 4.034em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 4.034em; top: -1.59em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">日志</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2.22</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 4.034em; bottom: -0.788em;"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">7</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 4.034em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.378em; vertical-align: -0.788em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">约</span></span><span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">11.4</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">%</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">年</span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>这是非常大的！事实上，它可能超过了全球<em>私人教育相关回报的</em>中位数。换句话说，如果你选取中等国家的人口并进行回归</p><p><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \log(\text{annual income}) = \alpha + \beta \times \text{years of education} + \varepsilon "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">日志</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">年收入</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.007em;">β</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">×</span></span> <span class="mjx-mtext MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">受教育年限</span></span><span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ε</span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>对于工作年龄的成年人，您可能会估计<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \beta \approx 0.1/\text{year} "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.007em;">β</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">≈</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.1</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">年</span></span></span></span></span></span>- 有关<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \beta "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.007em;">β</span></span></span></span></span></span>全球分布的更多信息，请参阅<a href="https://documents1.worldbank.org/curated/en/830831468147839247/pdf/WPS7020.pdf">Montenegro 和 Patrinos (2014)</a> 。因此，宾夕法尼亚大学世界表隐含地假设教育的社会回报等于私人相关回报，并忽略了我们有充分理由怀疑的重要影响：</p><ol><li><strong>能力偏见：</strong>受教育年限较长的人平均而言往往更有能力，因此他们在以后的生活中能够生产更多并赚取更多收入。</li><li><strong>信号效应：</strong>即使控制了能力偏差，我们也有<a href="http://www.bcaplan.com/returns.pdf">充分的理由</a>认为，一半或更多的教育回报来自信号效应，即人们收入更高，因为学位为雇主提供了清晰的能力、责任心、服从性信号<em>等等</em>。</li></ol><p>我认为教育社会回报的正确估计应该是宾夕法尼亚大学世界表所使用估计值的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 20 \% "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">20</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">%</span></span></span></span></span></span>或更少。我可以明确地进行此修正，但由于<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" 20 \% "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">20</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">%</span></span></span></span></span></span>接近于零，这与完全从 TFP 估计中删除人力资本调整相差不远，这就是我在上图中所做的。</p><h3>资本份额假设</h3><p>假设<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \alpha_K = 1 - \alpha_L "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.04em;">K</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>可能看起来合理，但事实上，它很可能被高估。可能还有其他生产要素，其中最重要的可能是农业社会中的土地，这表明这种方法会系统性地高估经济以农业为主且土地仍然是重要生产要素的贫穷国家的资本份额。虽然 PWT 在此计算中修正了自然资源租金，但并未修正土地应计租金。</p><p>纠正这种偏差应该会让我们估计出更高的全要素生产率增长率。事实上，如果我们带回关键身份</p><p><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label=" \frac{1}{Y} \frac{dY}{dt} = \frac{1}{A} \frac{dA}{dt} + \alpha_L \frac{1}{L} \frac{dL}{dt} + \alpha_K \frac{1}{K} \frac{dK}{dt} "><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.963em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 0.963em; top: -1.368em;"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 0.963em; bottom: -0.772em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.182em;">是</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.963em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.14em; vertical-align: -0.772em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.486em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 1.486em; top: -1.396em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">dYdt</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.182em;">_</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 1.486em; bottom: -0.795em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">_</span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.486em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.191em; vertical-align: -0.795em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.95em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 0.95em; top: -1.368em;"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1A</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 0.95em; bottom: -0.806em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">_</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.95em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.174em; vertical-align: -0.806em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.473em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 1.473em; top: -1.418em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">d</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">d</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 1.473em; bottom: -0.795em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span clas